{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "Differently from the described literature, in this study, we focused on generative AI and conversational systems applied to process-aware support systems.",
    "The main idea is that the emerging LLM technologies can contribute to improving process-based decision systems.",
    "According to this in a recent work [17] the possible implications of conversational systems applied to the process of decision support are discussed.",
    "The authors highlight the importance of transforming business questions and hypotheses written in natural language, into executable specifications able to generate relevant reports for the business stakeholders [18].",
    "The same authors highlight that conversational systems can also contribute to presenting the results of process mining analysis using a simple natural language by creating a process description from an event log, or a concise report describing the process performance [19][20][21]."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "According to this in a recent work [17] the possible implications of conversational systems applied to the process of decision support are discussed.",
